title: Min Yoongi (Suga):
body:
Jin | Suga | J-Hope | RM | Jimin | V | Jungkook

Yoongi is an Alpha werewolf, and is strongly regarded as the ‘strong and silent’ type of person. He will rarely get involved with others’ affairs, unless he can see something is about to go severely wrong. He is very observant, as he spends a lot of time on the side-lines, and can often detect something before it happens. He likes to just sit and watch his pack members from a distance, learning their habits and memorising their patterns. His quick instincts and ability to anticipate people’s actions make him the perfect protector, which he does proudly. He will often take late night shifts, watching the stillness of the forest for any sign of movement or, to be more specific, threats to his pack. As an Alpha he is a natural fighter, and is always willing to stand up for his pack, although he rarely attacks his opponents. His preferred tactic is to avoid attacks aimed at him and try to tire his opponent out, making him the most skilled fighter in the pack. He will often take the time to practice his skills with the other werewolves; both to teach them his methods and to improve them himself. He can sometimes appear cold and distant, but he is merely quiet and observant, and his pack know that he is always looking out for them.

Yoongi as a wolf is very quick, his movements almost undetectable. He is the most agile wolf in the pack, and also has the sharpest senses. These have developed from his years of sitting by and observing his surroundings. The wolf is always on guard, and it takes a really special moment to get him to completely relax. He is very wary of his environment, but is also very calculating and will rarely just charge into a fight without thinking of the consequences. On the whole Yoongi is a very sharp and cautious member of the pack.
